---
import PublicPagesLayout from '@layouts/PublicPagesLayout.astro';
import IconArrowRight from '@icons/IconArrowRight.astro';
---

<PublicPagesLayout
  title="Help Center — Bitcoin API"
  description="Find answers to common questions and get help with the Bitcoin API."
  tawk>
  <main class="py-16 lg:py-24">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold tracking-tight mb-4">Help Center</h1>
        <p class="text-lg text-[#565d6d] max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Everything you need to get started and make the most of Bitcoin API.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Quick links -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-20">
        <a href="/docs" class="group bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl border border-[#dee1e6]/50 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
          <h3 class="text-base font-semibold mb-2 group-hover:text-[#0983FD] transition-colors">Documentation</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-[#565d6d]">Guides, references, and examples to integrate the API.</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/docs/quickstart" class="group bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl border border-[#dee1e6]/50 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
          <h3 class="text-base font-semibold mb-2 group-hover:text-[#0983FD] transition-colors">Quickstart</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-[#565d6d]">Get your first API call running in under 5 minutes.</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/docs/authentication" class="group bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl border border-[#dee1e6]/50 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
          <h3 class="text-base font-semibold mb-2 group-hover:text-[#0983FD] transition-colors">Authentication</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-[#565d6d]">Learn how to authenticate your requests with API keys.</p>
        </a>
      </div>

      <!-- FAQ -->
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-8 mt-8">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>

        <div class="space-y-6">
          <details class="group bg-white rounded-xl border border-[#dee1e6]/50 shadow-sm">
            <summary class="flex items-center justify-between cursor-pointer p-6 text-base font-medium select-none">
              How do I get an API key?
              <IconArrowRight class="w-4 h-4 text-[#565d6d] transition-transform group-open:rotate-90" />
            </summary>
            <div class="px-6 pb-6 text-sm text-[#565d6d] leading-relaxed">
              Sign up for a free account and you'll receive an API key on your
              <a href="/profile/home" class="text-[#0983FD] hover:underline">profile dashboard</a>.
              You can use it immediately to start making requests.
            </div>
          </details>

          <details class="group bg-white rounded-xl border border-[#dee1e6]/50 shadow-sm">
            <summary class="flex items-center justify-between cursor-pointer p-6 text-base font-medium select-none">
              What are the rate limits?
              <IconArrowRight class="w-4 h-4 text-[#565d6d] transition-transform group-open:rotate-90" />
            </summary>
            <div class="px-6 pb-6 text-sm text-[#565d6d] leading-relaxed">
              Free-tier accounts can make up to 100 requests per minute. If you need higher limits, check our
              <a href="/pricing" class="text-[#0983FD] hover:underline">pricing page</a> for available plans.
            </div>
          </details>

          <details class="group bg-white rounded-xl border border-[#dee1e6]/50 shadow-sm">
            <summary class="flex items-center justify-between cursor-pointer p-6 text-base font-medium select-none">
              Which data sources do you use?
              <IconArrowRight class="w-4 h-4 text-[#565d6d] transition-transform group-open:rotate-90" />
            </summary>
            <div class="px-6 pb-6 text-sm text-[#565d6d] leading-relaxed">
              We aggregate data directly from centralized and decentralized exchanges as well as on-chain blockchain
              data. Source failover is automatic to ensure high availability.
            </div>
          </details>

          <details class="group bg-white rounded-xl border border-[#dee1e6]/50 shadow-sm">
            <summary class="flex items-center justify-between cursor-pointer p-6 text-base font-medium select-none">
              Is the API free to use?
              <IconArrowRight class="w-4 h-4 text-[#565d6d] transition-transform group-open:rotate-90" />
            </summary>
            <div class="px-6 pb-6 text-sm text-[#565d6d] leading-relaxed">
              Yes — we offer a generous free tier so you can start building without any cost. Paid plans are available
              when you need higher throughput or premium endpoints.
            </div>
          </details>

          <details class="group bg-white rounded-xl border border-[#dee1e6]/50 shadow-sm">
            <summary class="flex items-center justify-between cursor-pointer p-6 text-base font-medium select-none">
              How do I report a bug or request a feature?
              <IconArrowRight class="w-4 h-4 text-[#565d6d] transition-transform group-open:rotate-90" />
            </summary>
            <div class="px-6 pb-6 text-sm text-[#565d6d] leading-relaxed">
              Reach out via email at
              <a href="mailto:bshevchenko12@gmail.com" class="text-[#0983FD] hover:underline">bshevchenko12@gmail.com</a>
              or join our Discord community. We review every request.
            </div>
          </details>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Contact CTA -->
      <div class="mt-20 text-center bg-[#EFF6FF] rounded-2xl p-10">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Still need help?</h3>
        <p class="text-[#565d6d] mb-6">We're here to assist. Drop us a line and we'll get back to you shortly.</p>
        <button
          data-open-tawk
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-[#0983FD] text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-md text-sm font-medium shadow-sm hover:bg-[#076ed4]">
          Contact Support
          <IconArrowRight class="w-4 h-4" />
        </button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</PublicPagesLayout>
